To start using the JS hooks, you'll need only to create `*.pb.js` file(s) inside a `pb_hooks` directory.
You can put all your hooks inside a single file or split it in multiple files.
There is a file watcher that will restart the application if `pb_hooks` changes (currently supported only on UNIX based systems).
